# Application Setup

## Access the Application

- The frontend will be accessible at: [http://localhost:3001](http://localhost:3001).
- The backend API will be accessible at: [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000).

## Environment Variables

### Frontend

- `API_URL`: Backend API base URL (set in `.env` file).

### Backend

- `RAILS_ENV`: Rails environment (default: `development`).
- `PORT`: Backend application port (default: `3000`).

## Kubernetes Deployment

To deploy the application in a Kubernetes cluster:

1. Navigate to the `kubernetes/` directory:
   ```bash
   cd kubernetes/

2. Apply the Kubernetes manifests:
    kubectl apply -f .